ath</strong><br></li><li>Unlock Boss Relics with run-changing effects</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/bossSkelly.gif?t=1726299113\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/storeBuild.png?t=1726299113\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unlock multiple heroes with different unique attacks<br></li><li>Collect gems to level up your hero, add or modify attacks<br></li><li>Experiment with an endless combination of effects</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/gifMobs.gif?t=1726299113\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/storeDeep.png?t=1726299113\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Spend gold between runs to unlock new gameplay options<br></li><li>Increase the power of Relics found within the dungeons</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/storeCoop.png?t=1726299113\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Team up to crush your enemies with local co-op<br></li><li>Steam Remote Play compatible<br></li><li>Requires controller for second player</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2027510/extras/wizSkull.png?t=1726299113\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Master Warrior","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2027510/ced1192a3d65087df5b534441b4f1e2bb3ad2194.jpg"},{"name":"Master Ranger","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2027510/a5c8591486bcdb5dbf427e1346cf226d96dc4fbf.jpg"},{"name":"Master Wizard","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2027510/8e623d9a3748d81cc88bb4fca1e82644bbb9b4e1.jpg"},{"name":"M